subject: Raw files from plane crash ITC sessions
author: M.A. Coletta (Mike)
full_text:
Greetings fellow researchers,

In my continuing quest to openly share what I do, I've completed 
uploading 36 files from the numerous ITC sessions I performed durng my 
plane crash paranormal investigation. (Raw files and processed files)
If you're interested in hearing or experimenting with any of the files, 
please be my guest. They are located at the following link, at the top 
of the page:

http://www.ufogeek.com/vftse.htm

Also on that page are the videos of what I did. The Youtube multiple 
segments are listed in order, first... and the entire 43 minute video 
is at the bottom.

Thanks... and have a great day!
- Mike C. (UFO Geek)
http://www.ufogeek.com
